    "This extends towards exploring how GPTs can facilitate immersive experiences through virtual and augmented reality in the tourism domain.",
    "Tackling ethical considerations and biases embedded within GPT models is of paramount importance.",
    "Research should explore methodologies for identifying, quantifying, and mitigating biases in GPT outputs and ensuring that its interactions and recommendations adhere to ethical guidelines and are free from discriminatory or biased undertones.",
    "In summary, enhancing the adoption and efficacy of GPTs in tourism requires a holistic approach, amalgamating technological advancements with user-centric, ethical, and contextually apt considerations.",
    "As we forge into the future, ensuring that GPT applications are adaptable, reliable, inclusive, and ethically grounded will be pivotal in harnessing their full potential in enhancing global tourism experiences."
